Quick before the price goes up to $3 like the first one cuz I feel like I'm playing an expensive game not a $1 title so worth 99 pennies this will make u think harder in a good way not the frustrating impossible to figure out kind of way either and it's such a value cuz the fun never ends with the level editor u can create and share levels with the community and that there is worth a buck I can't believe I never heard of this it's one of the best games I ever picked up I never heard of the first game I guess cuz of angry birds but this blows that game out of the water and even contre jour I wish I had known about this and gotten it first cuz with this u don't need any other puzzle game in the app store cuz this never ends and has raised the bar forever and everything works well there are lots of elements such as the fast paint bomb bouncy paint and sticky paint and then setting the timer on them to go off for the correct time there's tons of trial and error but it's fun and has dots to show u were u were last and it helps alot when ur trying to figure out were to place something 
THE ONLY WAY THIS COULD IMPROVE IS TO ADD A FASTFORWARD TIME BUTTON for multiple tries on a ten second fuse can waste alot of time so PLEASE ADD THAT FAST BUTTON IN AN UPDATE FOR THE LONG FUSES. 
But it's not hurting the game at all so far and I'm only on the first world there's 60 levels by the devs per world and like 7-9worlds maybe with more to come and in the mean time u can just have a blast (pun intended) lol making and sharing and trying an endless amount of user created worlds and levels this game truly is infinite as people make it and there's already alot of levels created the game has such a high polish and just has fun written all over it I wish more devs would take the time to put this much into all games. And I never played the first game probably don't need to unless u absolutely want to but if ur into puzzles which I'm not too big on at all so I found myself pleasantly surprised by how 3 hrs went by and I was still playing this and I haven't even seen 10% of this games potential yet. If ur on the fence about any puzzle game or getting a great game for a buck get this u won't regret it there's so much wonderful and fun content cuz this is the type of puzzle that moves u don't sit in one place the levels have curves and u fly around and it's awesome and when u beat a level it compares ur score to the top 3 in the world it's fun when u get really close and u can even watch how others have beaten a level. Right now this game is so feature rich it's a steel at $1 get it before it goes up and u will regret that when this kills angrybirds the depth alone plus angrybirds is too stationary and repetitive this is always new each level way different then the last top ten and should be up for game of the year for sure

This isn't anywhere close to an angry birds adaptation, it's a completely different kind of game.

I always finish the levels in the most crazy ways possible, I dunno its like if u move one thing the slightest bit it changes the whole outcome.  I think some of my videos should get posted just cus I do things in a way better looking way than people that just take the easiest way possible, I still get 3 stars I'm just saying u should also get points for creativity not just speed.  So instead just gettting to watch 5 or so people do the same thing u could get to see people doing it different ways. 

I don't really even care about the points, I just wanna show people some of the ridiculously crazy ways I've been able to beat some levels.  The makers always do it the simple way and other people the fastest way, I like to get creative...  

That's the beauty of this game there's no right way to beat a level so it's up to u....  I spend hours just on one level playing around with things.

This another one of those games I could play forever and never get bored... There's only a few of those games.

This game has to be up for Up for Goty. I dunno I guess since I never played the first one I like it alot more since it feels completely new. 

Thats about it this game is a must have IMO, not for kids or people that that don't have patience or time, it takes a while to learn the basics and then applying it takes even longer. 

I dunno I guess some people don't like having to use their brains too much or it isn't fun. 

I hope to see some additional content in levels or more items or whatever. Maybe being able too look at more variety of peoples levels.   

If I have any more ideas I'll post them, I was thinking of an idea to go into a level with prepicked items or random some how.... Since levels can be beaten so many different ways I thinks it good idea too add more depth somehow. 

For multiplayer maybe have a time limit or bases on how many tries, maybe playing on the same level vs or separate or a diff. Level. Or maybe coop with people solving one puZle together with them each only being to able to use Thier own diffent items and then using them to combine stuff, except the player that's not pressing go can move or set up stuff while in action then the chatactwr just stays wheee he ends up unless he dies etc... I dunno just some vague ideas probly to complicated.... Oh well 

Buy this game ASAP, before u get anything else....
